Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個先待在那裏待命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷並無入□
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其入□是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舵…舵無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力計破表了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯的遭到遺忘之都城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是幻之谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏究竟是個什麼樣的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我在梵瀕臨死亡時所預見到的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母后?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過去,謝蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯文字的石碑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是亞特蘭提斯的遺跡\N幻之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道上面寫著什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新星運記,十三之月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得懂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等亞特蘭提斯末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為龍神人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生於位在幻之月的亞特蘭提斯之都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻…幻之月?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯是幻之月之民?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量強大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並自封為超越神明之存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造出不祥之機械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此機械可將人的意念轉化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所不知,無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至讓自己背上生出羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了自身的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個墜子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠的意念讓天空中出現一顆新星"蓋亞"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃亞特蘭提斯之意念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"愚昧我等所造就出的過往不會再重複"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含著此一令人傷感之願
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是顆為天擁抱,為水所愛,為大地所滋養的美麗星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋亞是由意念之力所創?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將意念轉化成力量的機械?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所謂的亞特蘭提斯之謎嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我交給她的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那是前世的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是龍神人染滿鮮血的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流於梵大人體內之血的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您必須正視自己的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍神人為亞特蘭提斯的末裔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不使蓋亞步上亞特蘭提斯的後塵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您注定要與其相抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您得與艾斯嘉科尼一同戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵跟亞連他們都在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟看到了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我的願望終於實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…該從什麼開始說好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今,還有什麼好說的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你當上天空騎士了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親她一定很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親…安希亞過得好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你外出旅行的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希亞她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要哭?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要痛失所愛之人都會流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不愛她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,一直,憎恨著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,狀況似乎不太穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去我們恐怕很難離開這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏雖然是蓋亞卻也不是蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你沒有辦法嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請引導梵,亞連還有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以使用意念之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意念源自於不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股意念會讓不安成為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意念…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在折磨梵他們的其實就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為自己占卜到的是未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實不然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我害的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不安的內心藉由占卜憎強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在數種未來當中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇了悲傷的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,你的心目前仍充滿了不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我將不幸的未來吸引過來的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是因為我的意念…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正在追殺從幻之谷出來的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要知道亞特蘭提斯之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多倫卡喀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經拿到那樣東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我費了那麼多工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失去家庭,丟掉性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不肯將幻之谷的秘密告訴我是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞特蘭提斯之力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意念的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我見那名少女一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會還保持著那時候的模樣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的亞特蘭提斯之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的意念之力,原來是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候果然沒想錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能帶著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念會成真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便相隔遙遠也能穿越時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越時空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,安希亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到死都還愛著父親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而父親您其實也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直愛著她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又為什麼要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了家庭而結婚生子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾打算壓抑自己,就這麼過一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人就是會有股想要逃離既有命運的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次見到那名少女時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都愛著安希亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人真是愚昧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼亞特蘭提斯之力,什麼意念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻連自己的想法都沒弄懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安希亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你要對自己坦承一點
