Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧您平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於回來了
