Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來試試看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅機,耶莉雅機上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝亞特蘭提斯之門接近
